151
00:05:40,276 --> 00:05:41,867
Let's do this.

152
00:05:41,870 --> 00:05:43,302
Right.

153
00:05:47,483 --> 00:05:49,450
Enjoy the show, Dad.

154
00:05:49,452 --> 00:05:51,085
[WINGS WHOOSH]

155
00:05:56,192 --> 00:05:59,126
[HEART RATE MONITOR FLATLINING]

156
00:05:59,128 --> 00:06:01,095
- [WIND WHOOSHES]
- [FEET THUD]

157
00:06:01,097 --> 00:06:03,015
Right.

158
00:06:05,735 --> 00:06:09,303
